OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms could have energy    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbills cut by up to a third 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Businesses could have their energy     
OL,6, bills cut by a third under government  
OL,7, support to be announced later.         
OL,9,FBusiness Secretary Jacob Rees-Mogg is  
OL,10,Fexpected to reveal a cap on wholesale  
OL,11,Fenergy costs for business customers.   
OL,13,FIt is thought the limit will be 21.1p  
OL,14,Fper kWh for electricity and 7.5p per   
OL,15,FKWh for gas - a discount of a quarter  
OL,16,Fto a third on current market prices.   
OL,18,FIt means businesses facing an energy   
OL,19,Fbill of #40,000 could see a reduction  
OL,20,Fof #10,000 depending on usage patterns.
